@henryfhchan The problem raised by 14-006 is, there should be a way to provide such l. info for higher levels when l. tags r not applicable.
@henryfhchan I know fonts better than u. Lang tags r where layout or text engines can get the lang info and choose a suitable font or glyph.
@henryfhchan Because 象棋 symbols do have a more general look that can be generalized and fit in the existing set of circled characters.
